title: Temur Maghradze Stadium
text: Temur Maghradze Stadium is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Chiatura">Chiatura</a>, <a href="Imereti">Imereti</a> region, <a href="Georgia%20%28country%29">Georgia</a>. It is used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="FC%20Chiatura">FC Chiatura</a>. The stadium is able to hold 11,650 people.
